:name:
Celeritas

:coretxt:
Vampire posses mystical inhuman speed.
This secret can be taken several times.
Using this secret imposes penalty to opponent in combat, instead of bonus die to user.

:cost:
Vigor

:req:
Has raced against rising sun

:1:
Able to move at speed 50km/h.

:2:
Able to move at speed 80km/h.

:3:
Able to move at speed 130km/h.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricStrength
